	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64287888"><p>I know what things look like, but I don't see any "pictures". If I try, I can call up a very vague and fleeting visual impression, but it takes a specific effort, and is gone in a fraction of a second. I do dream visually, sometimes with more detail, sometimes with less.

</p><p>The author writes "I can remember visual details, just not visually." Exactly. But that probably makes zero sense to people who can see images.</p></div>
	</div>

