	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64288060"><p>Note that when aphantasia was discovered by Francis Galton in 1880, he found that MOST of the scientists that he knew had it.  So, while we're only 2% of the population, we are extremely overrepresented in engineering, sciences, and some arts.</p><p>I'm a classic example.  I'm an engineer ("senior software architect"), and, as is common for aphantasia, I depend on creating extremely detailed technical diagrams of my designs, since I can't "see it in my mind."  That led to gaining my roles.  Also, typical of aphant<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

